    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything feels so pointless lately. i keep looking at the news and seeing the climate data and the ecosystem collapse and it just feels like we're all just living in a burning house. like, why even bother trying to build a life or plan for a future when the planet is basically already dead? it feels like everything we do is just delaying the inevitable. i'm just so tired of pretending it matters.",
