      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that \"small actions\" stuff feels like just putting a band-aid on a severed limb. it's all just distraction. how can people actually sleep at night knowing the math doesn't add up? it feels so much more honest to just admit that there's no real way out and everything is just a slow decay. it's exhausting to keep fighting a battle that was lost decades ago.",
