      "content": "i hear you, but \"witnessing it\" just feels like watching a tragedy play out in slow motion. it feels so much more logical to just not be around for the end of it. if the outcome is already decided, why stay to watch the wreckage? it seems like the only way to actually find peace is to just stop participating in a system that's doomed to fail.",
